{"id":587108,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/06/【图说天朝】日本大阪发生6-1级地震后/","date":"2018-06-18T06:13:37Z","modified":"2018-06-18T06:50:35Z","title":"【图说天朝】日本大阪发生6.1级地震后","content":"<p>日本当地时间6月18日早上7时58分（北京时间6时58分），以大阪府北部为震源发生里氏6.1级地震，截至目前已造成1名9岁女孩死亡、数人重伤，没有引发海啸，核电站并未发现异常。</p>\n<p>地震发生后，一些官方微博（环球时报、人民日报等）评论处，再度出现许多中国网友“叫好”声。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/Df8bF44VQAAbNT_.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-587109\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/Df8bF44VQAAbNT_.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"454\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/Df8bF44VQAAbNT_.jpg 750w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/Df8bF44VQAAbNT_-150x150.jpg 150w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/Df8bF44VQAAbNT_-298x300.jpg 298w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/Df8bF44VQAAbNT_-70x70.jpg 70w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/Df8bF44VQAAbNT_-50x50.jpg 50w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a> <a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/Df8vU9zW0AIQ1mn.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-587110\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/Df8vU9zW0AIQ1mn.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"800\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/Df8vU9zW0AIQ1mn.jpg 675w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/Df8vU9zW0AIQ1mn-169x300.jpg 169w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/Df8vU9zW0AIQ1mn-576x1024.jpg 576w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a> <a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/Df8vU9zXkAEeMmo.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-587111\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/Df8vU9zXkAEeMmo.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"800\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/Df8vU9zXkAEeMmo.jpg 675w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/20